verses.verse: Sing to the LORD with the harp, With the harp and the sound of a psalm,
With trumpets and the sound of a horn; Shout joyfully before the LORD, the King.
Let the sea roar, and all its fullness, The world and those who dwell in it;
Let the rivers clap their hands; Let the hills be joyful together before the LORD,
((Ps. 96:10, 13)) For He is coming to judge the earth. With righteousness He shall judge the world, And the peoples with equity.
